title: Looking for High Elo Scrim!!!
body:
Hello guys!

I know its probably a little short to ask now, but im looking for a High Elo Scrim Partner which is supposed to play against a Team which will compete in the next ESLM qualifier. The players are actually between D3 and Master (SoloQ ranks of course) and the scrim would be tomorrow at 5 p.m. CET on the EUW server. 

If you're interested or if there are any additional questions, please add me ingame. Im available pretty much anytime.

AI Holo
